high_descs: Turn left and go straight towards the wall. Then, hang left and walk straight into the room and turn to the sofa on your right
Pick up apple from the sofa
Turn around and make a straight turn before proceeding to turn left towards the fridge
Place apple inside the fridge and then take it out
Turn right and go straight and make a right turn near microwave
anns.task_desc: Place apple inside fridge and placing it in microwave

high_descs: Walk across the room to the sofa.
Pick up the apple that is on the plate.
Take the apple with you to the kitchen and go in front of the fridge.
Put the apple in the fridge, open the fridge and take the apple back out.
Take the apple to the microwave.
Open the microwave and put the apple in it.
anns.task_desc: Moving the apple from the sofa to the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around, walk over to the far end of the sofa.
Pick up the apple from the plate on the couch.
Walk through the door into the kitchen then over to the fridge.
Open the refrigerator door, then place the apple on the second shelf and close the door, then open the door again and retrieve the apple.
Move over to the microwave beside the fridge.
Place the apple into the microwave and close the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Cool off an apple in the refrigerator to put into the microwave.
